    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-07-01T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-07-01T16:00:00-05:00" n="192"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d192">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">330/6–2850: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">United States Mission at the United Nations</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-07-01T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 1, 1950—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> expects provide full reply questions
                    raised Para 5(<hi rend="italic">a</hi>) ur 554 Jun 28 soonest possible.
                    Meanwhile fol present gen views <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> may be
                    helpful.</p>
                <p>Action to prevent attack on Formosa and to prevent Natl Govt air and sea
                    operations against mainland taken as immediate security measure to preserve
                    peace in Pacific and without prejudice to pol questions affecting Chi Govt. No
                    change anticipated in relations between US Govt and Chi Govt.</p>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> believes Amb Gross expressed this very
                    well in his conversation with Lie (ur 569 June 30<note n="1" xml:id="d192fn1"
                        >Not printed.</note>) when he pointed out US move respecting Formosa of mil
                    significance only and believes <gloss target="#t_USUN1">USUN</gloss> shld
                    continue adhere this explanation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
